  (text "IO: slot connector split into power blades (>=30A, first-mate/last-break) +\nsignal row (CAN, HW_EN, slot straps, PRESENT->PGND). Physical connector family\nchosen at the batch PCB pass with the backplane (docs/08 s.12) - generic\nheaders stand in so the netlist is final. Fan: 5V, low-side PWM switch." (at 15.24 33.02 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 0303224c-854d-4915-9c9f-ab05cea0ee65))
